{"id": "1234833214711791678", "channel_id": "1227715220613365790", "type": 19, "author_id": "1180456731143327794", "author_name": "su_su_su0216", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果担心会不小心把命定消耗掉，可以不放回环的命定，力量和力量倍率叠的高的话不回环也有很不错的输出", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T11:46:20.479000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1230083504285421578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1234669689263751209", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1227715220613365790", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉环娜主c攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1234838484909293568", "channel_id": "1227715220613365790", "type": 19, "author_id": "1230083504285421578", "author_name": "qingshanzhiyin", "author_bot": false, "content": "假如我已经把命定消耗掉了，环娜开大招召回后，我留着命定之剑不打出去或者打出的最后三张牌里面没有命定，这样牌库里还有吗？", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T12:07:16.992000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1180456731143327794"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1234833214711791678", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1227715220613365790", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉环娜主c攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
