{"id": "1234903750959956138", "channel_id": "1227715220613365790", "type": 19, "author_id": "1230083504285421578", "author_name": "qingshanzhiyin", "author_bot": false, "content": "按lz的说法，最后三张牌打防超越命定，超越应该抓什么牌啊？那抓了牌不就不算最后3张嘛？难不成不打出去", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T16:26:37.631000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1180456731143327794"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1234891199039410208", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1227715220613365790", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉环娜主c攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
